__gh__webApp.ads.dfp.slot.loadInjected(slotToInject);
</script><p>But the Superwomen app isn’t for everybody. “It’s for girls only,” Grady said. If you’re a boy, the app will kick you out. (How that would work, exactly, she said, is a technical challenge for down the road.)</p><p>For more information visit the YWCA’s <a href="http://www.ywcari.org/" target="_blank">webpage</a> and click on the Fantastic Girltastic Code Company or call (401) 769-7450.</p><p><em><a href="mailto:%E2%80%94larditi@providencejournal.com">—larditi@providencejournal.com</a></em></p><p><em>(401) 277-7335</em></p><p><em>On Twitter: <a href="http://www.twitter.com/LynnArditi" target="_blank">@LynnArditi</a></em></p>
		
		
		
		
